        "content": "<p>Among <code>Finset</code>s, I don't seem to find one. The proof is fairly simple.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">theorem</span> <span class=\"n\">Finset.card_eq_card_sdiff_add_card_inter</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Finset</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">x.card</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">\\</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">card</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">∩</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">card</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">rw</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span> <span class=\"n\">card_disjoint_union</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">disjoint_sdiff_inter</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"n\">sdiff_union_inter</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>If there's none, I'd like to add this lemma to <code>Data.Finset.Card</code>.<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/7605\">github</a></p>",
